(8, '\nOomakkuyil Padumbol\n', 'http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/5/5b/OomakkuyilPadumbol.jpeg/220px-OomakkuyilPadumbol.jpeg', 'The story is about Reema (Malavika Nair), a young Muslim schoolgirl in Malabar, who loved Malayalam and poetry. The film is about her mental trauma once she was moved to an English medium school by her parents, for their social status.[2]', '0000-00-00', 0, 1, 0),
