(48, '\nPriyam\n', 'http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/bc/Indiafilm.png/16px-Indiafilm.png', 'The story of three spoilt brats and their uncle, Benny (Kunchacko Boban). Benny was brought up in an orphanage with his best friend, Annie. Her Dad(Devan), realising his greatest asset needs to be with him always separates them. Annie vows to get back to benny. She hoping benny would realise her love joins the three brats and him as their caretaker. Not soon does she find that N.F.Varghese and his daughter decides to hire benny as his son-in-law and worker for the debt which the family owned.[2]', '0000-00-00', 0, 1, 1),
